hadiths[36]{hadithnumber,text}:
1861,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har nasha aawar chiz sharab hai aur har nasha aawar chiz haram hai, jisney duniya mein sharab pi aur wo us haal mein mar gaya ke wo uska aadi tha, to wo aakhirat mein isey nahin piyega. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees kaee sanadon sey Nafey sey aai hai, jisey Nafey , ibne-Umar sey , ibne-Umar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain. 3- Malik bin Anas ney is hadees ko Nafey key wastey sey ibne-Umar sey mauqufan riwayat ki hai. isey marfoo nahin kiya hai. 4- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , abu Saeed Khudri , Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas , ibne-Abbas , Ubada aur abu Malik Ash-ari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1862,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney sharab pi Allah Taala uski chaalis din ki namaz qubul nahin kerega, agar wo tauba kar ley to Allah uski tauba qubul kerega, agar usney dobara sharab pi to Allah Taala uski chaalis din ki namaz qubul nahin kerega, agar wo tauba kar ley to Allah uski tauba qubul kerega, agar usney phir sharab pi to Allah Taala uski chaalis din ki namaz qubul nahin kerega, agar wo tauba kar ley to Allah uski tauba qubul kerega, agar usney chauthi baar bhi sharab pi to Allah Taala uski chaalis din ki namaz qubul nahin kerega aur agar wo tauba karey to uski tauba bhi qubul nahin kerega, aur us ko nehar khabaal sey pilaaeyga, puchha gaya, abu-Abdur-Rehman ! nehar khabaal kya hai? unhoney kaha : jahannamiyon key peep ki eik nehar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas aur ibne-Abbas key wastey sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
1863,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey shehad ki nabeez key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : ''har sharab jo nasha paida kar dey wo haram hai.''Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1864,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey huye suna : ''har nasha aawar chiz haram hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- abu-Salma sey Abu-Hurera key wastey sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai, dono hadisein sahih hain, kaee logon ney isey isi tarah (Muhammad bin Amr an abi Salama an abi Huraira an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) aur (an abi Salma an ibne-Umar an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein umr , Ali , ibne-Masood , Anas , abu Saeed Khudri , abu-Musa Ashajj, Asri ,  Memuna , ibne-Abbas , Qais bin Saad , Noman bin Bashir , Muawiya , Wayl bin Hajar , Qurra Muzni , Abdullah bin Mughaffal , Umme-Salma , Barida , Abu-Hurera aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees (hadeesen) aai hain."
1865,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis chiz ki ziyada miqdaar nasha paida kar dey to uski thodi si miqdaar bhi haram hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Jabir ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Saad , Aaisha , Abdullah bin Amr , ibne-Umar aur Khuwaat bin Juber (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1866,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''har nasha aawar chiz haram hai, jis chiz ka eik farq (sola ritl ya chaalis tole) ki miqdaar bhar nasha paida kar dey to uski mutthi bhar miqdaar bhi haram hai padhi. , un mein (yani Muhammad bin Bashaar aur Abdullah bin Muawiya Jamhi) mein sey eik ney apni riwayat mein kaha : yani uska eik ghoont bhi haram hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- isey Les bin abi Sulem aur Rabee bin Sabeeh ney abu-Usman Ansari sey Mehdi bin Memun ki hadees jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai."
1867,"eik aadmi ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key paas aaya aur puchha : kya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney matkey ki nabeez sey mana farmaya hai? unhoney kaha : haan padhi. , Taaus kehtey hain : Allah ki qism mainey un sey ye baat suni hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abi Aufi , abu Saeed Khudri , Suwed , Aaisha , ibne Zuber aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1868,"mainey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey un bartanon key mutalliq puchha jin sey aap ney mana farmaya hai aur kaha is ko apni zaban mein bayan kijiye aur hamari zaban mein uski tashreeh keejiye, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (hantama) sey mana farmaya hai aur wo matka hai, aap ney (dubbaa) sey mana farmaya hai aur wo kaddu ki tonbi hai. aap ney (naqeer) sey mana farmaya aur wo khajoor ki jad hai jis ko andar sey gehra kar key ya khraad kar bartan bana letey hain, aap ney (muzaffat) sey mana farmaya aur wo raughane-qeer mila huwa (laakhi) bartan hai, aur aap ney hukm diya ke nabeez mashkon mein banai jaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein umr , Ali , ibne-Abbas , abu Saeed Khudri , Abu-Hurera , Abdur-Rehman bin Yaamar, Samura , Anas , Aaisha , Imran bin Husain , Aaid bin Amr , Hukm Ghifaari aur Memuna (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1869,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney tumhen (is sey pehley baab ki hadees mein mazkur (zikr hue)) bartanon sey mana kiya tha, dar-haqiqat bartan kisi chiz ko na to halal kartey hain na haram (balke) har nasha aawar chiz haram hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1870,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (in) bartanon ( key istimal ( sey mana farmaya to ansaar ney aap sey shikayat ki, aur kaha : hamarey paas doosrey bartan nahin hain, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tab main mana nahin karta.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , abu Saeed Khudri , Abu-Hurera aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1871,"hum log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key liye mashk mein nabeez banatey they, uskey ooper ka munh band kar diya jata tha, uskey nichey eik surakh hota tha, hum subah mein nabeez ko bhigotey they to aap Sham ko peetey they aur Sham ko bhigotey they to aap subah ko peetey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey Yunus bin Ubaid ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey ye hadees dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai. 3- is bab mein Jabir , abu-Saeed aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1872,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''gehun , jo , khajoor , kishmish , aur shehad sey sharab banai jati hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera sey bhi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai. faeyda padhi. : yani agar in chizon mein nasha paida ho jaey to wo sharab hai."
1873,usi jaisi hadees bayan ki.
1874,"sharab gehun sey banai jati hai, phir unhoney puri hadees bayan ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke gehun sey sharab banai jati hai, ye Ibrahim bin Muhajir ki riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai. 2- Ali bin Madeeni kehtey hain : Yahya bin Saeed ney kaha : Ibrahim bin Muhajir hadees bayan karney mein qawi nahin hain. 3- ye hadees dusri sanadon sey bhi Noman bin Bashir sey aai hai."
1875,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sharab in do darakhton : khajoor aur angoor sey banti hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Shoba ney Ikrima bin Ammar sey ye hadees riwayat ki hai.
1876,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (gaddar) (Adhpakki) khajoor aur taza khajoor ko mila kar nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1877,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney (gaddar) (adhpaki) khajoor aur pukhta khajoor eik sath mila kar nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya : ''aur aap ney matkon mein nabeez bananey sey mana farmaya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir , Anas , abu-Qatada , ibne-Abbas , Umme-Salma aur (معبد بن کعب an أمہ) (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1878,"Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik aadmi sey pani talab kiya to usney unhen chaandi key bartan mein pani diya, unhoney pani ko uskey munh par phenk diya, aur kaha : main is sey mana kar chuka tha, phir bhi is ney baaz rehney sey inkar kiya padhi. , beshak Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney soney aur chaandi key bartan mein pani peeney sey mana farmaya hai, aur resham pehanney sey aur deebaaj sey, aur farmaya : ''ye un (kafiron) key liye duniya mein hai aur tumharey liye aakhirat mein hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Umme-Salma , Bara , aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey ahadees aai hain."
1879,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khadey ho kar peeney sey mana farmaya , puchha gaya : khadey ho kar khana kaisa hai? kaha : ''ye aur bura hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1880,hum log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamane mein chaltey huye khatey they aur khadey ho kar peetey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees (Ubaidullah bin umr an Nafey an ibne-Umar) ki sanad sey sahih gharib hai. 2- Imran bin Hudair ney is hadees ko Abul Bazri key wastey sey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat ki hai. 3- Abul Bazri ka naam Yazeed bin Utaarid hai.
1881,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khadey ho kar peeney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib Hasan hai. 2- isi tarah kaee logon ney is hadees ko :(عن سعيد an قتادة an أبي مسلم an الجارود an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey riwayat kiya hai, aur ye hadees ba-tareeq : (عن قتادة an يزيد بن عبد الله ابن الشخير an أبي مسلم an الجارود أن النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki gaee hai ke aap ney farmaya : ''musalman ki giri hui chiz (yani is par qabza karney ki niyat sey) uthana aag mein jalney ka sabab hai.''  3- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri , Abu-Hurera aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1882,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney khadey ho kar zamzam ka pani piya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Saad , Abdullah bin Amr aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1883,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko khadey ho kar aur beth kar pani peetey dekha padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1884,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bartan sey teen saans mein pani peetey they aur farmatey they : (pani peeney ka ye tariqa ( ''ziyada khushgawar aur sairab kun hota hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- isey Hisham Dustwaai ney bhi Abu Isaam key wastey sey Anas sey riwayat ki hai, aur Azra bin Sabit ney Samaama sey , Samaama ney Anas sey riwayat ki hai, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bartan sey teen saans mein pani peetey they."
1885,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''oont ki tarah eik saans mein na piyo, balke do ya teen saans mein piyo, jab piyo to (Bismillah) kaho aur jab munh sey bartan hataao to (Alhamdulillah) kaho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai."
1886,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab peetey they to do saans mein peetey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Rushdain bin Kureb ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 3- mainey abu Muhammad Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman Darmi sey Rushdain bin Kureb key barey mein poochhtey huye kaha : wo ziyada qawi hain ya Muhammad bin Kuraib? unhoney kaha : dono (rutbe mein) bahut hi qarib hain, aur merey nazdik Rushdain bin Kureb ziyada raajeh (ziyada sahi) hain. 4- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey iskey barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : Muhammad bin Kureb , Rushdain bin Kureb sey ziyada raajeh (behtar) hain. 5- merey nazdik abu Muhammad Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman Darmi ki baat ziyada sahih hai ke Rushdain bin Kureb ziyada raajeh aur badey hain, unhoney ibne-Abbas ko paya hai aur unhen dekha hai, ye dono bhai hain in dono sey munkir hadeesen bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hain."
1887,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney peeney ki chiz mein phoonkney sey mana farmaya , eik aadmi ney arz kiya : bartan mein koi naa-pasandida chiz dekhun to kya karun? aap ney farmaya : ''usey baha do, usney arz kya : main eik saans mein sairab nahin ho paata hun, aap ney farmaya : ''tab (saans letey waqt) piyala apney munh sey hata lo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1888,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bartan mein saans leney aur phoonkney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1889,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi pani piye to bartan mein saans na chhodey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1890,"(Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney) mishkeezon sey munh laga kar peeney sey mana kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir , ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1891,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha , aap eik latki hui mishkeeza key paas gaey, usey jhukaya , phir uskey munh sey pani piya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Umme Sulem sey bhi riwayat hai (jo aagey aa rahi hai). 2- is hadees ki sanad sahih nahin hai, Abdullah bin umr hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain, main nahin janta hun ke unhoney Esa sey hadees suni hai ya nahin."
1892,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey ghar tashrif laye, aap ney eik latki hui mishkeeze key munh sey khadey ho kar pani piya , phir main mishkeeze key munh key paas gaee aur us ko kaat liya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
1893,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein doodh pesh kiya gaya jis mein pani mila huwa tha, aap key daain taraf eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) tha aur baain abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) , aap ney doodh piya , phir (bacha huwa doodh) Erabi (dehati) ko diya aur farmaya : ''daeyn taraf wala ziyada mustahiq hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Sehal bin Saad , ibne-Umar aur Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1894,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' pilaney waley ko sab sey aakhir mein peena chaahiye.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abi Aufi sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1895,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko mitha aur thanda mashrub sab sey ziyada pasand tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ibn Uena sey kaee logon ney isi tarah (an Maamar an Zohri an Urwaa an Aaysha) riwayat ki hai, lekin sahih wohi hai jo Zohri key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan marvi (riwayat hui) hai (jo aagey aa rahi hai)."
1896,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha gaya : kon sa mashrub behtar hai? aap ney farmaya : ''mitha aur thanda mashrub.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- isi tarah Abdur-Razzaaq ney bhi Maamar sey , Maamar ney Zohri sey aur Zohri ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam mursalan riwayat ki hai. 2- ye ibne Uena (Reh.) ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai."
